com.sonymobile.tools.xappdbg.properties
Class ClassItems

java.lang.Object
  com.sonymobile.tools.xappdbg.properties.ClassItems

public class ClassItems
extends java.lang.Object

This class stores all the items connected to one single class. For example it can contain all the properties of android.widget.TextView. Note that it does not care about other classes, like the super class, so inherited properties will be listed here as well.
